{"type":"message","id":"1225b972","parentId":"60ad2454","timestamp":"2026-03-24T19:49:34.754Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Seems to hang. Let me try to check if the gateway service is running another way. Let me also check if there's any recent error in the cron health. Let me also check moltbook since that was recent but I should verify if there are new notifications.\n\nActually, looking at the heartbeat state - the gateway check was last done at 1774369457 (which is in the future from current time perspective, but that's the timestamp from when it was last checked). The sandbox pulse just ran successfully according to the system message. The gateway might be running fine - the status command just hangs because it's waiting for something.\n\nLet me check if there are any recent cron errors by looking at any log files.","thinkingSignature":"cd6de3a17c3217b28a4514765c95cbc30db279609e403e69fa4e65852fefb02b"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_fys63t3kfhwh_1","name":"process","arguments":{"action":"poll","sessionId":"fresh-fjord","timeout":5000}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1346,"output":191,"cacheRead":11253,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":12790,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774381769636}}
