{"type":"message","id":"f3c6ab51","parentId":"b34946c5","timestamp":"2026-03-24T19:49:58.919Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Gateway port not found in netstat output. But the sandbox pulse ran. This might mean the gateway isn't running, but the pulse was triggered through a different mechanism (Task Scheduler direct or something).\n\nActually, let me look at the system message again: \"Exec completed (rapid-ne, code 0) :: > applied}/2026-03-24 154717.mutation (100%) [sandbox pulse]\"\n\nThis shows a sandbox pulse was executed (rapid-ne is a session ID, code 0 means success). The pulse found something about CFI compression synthesis. This is noteworthy - it relates to one of Zach's active projects (EXP/CAAE).\n\nSince:\n1. Gateway command hangs (possible issue)\n2. But sandbox pulse ran successfully\n3. The pulse found something interesting about CFI compression synthesis\n\nI think I should mention the CFI findings to Zach since it's technically interesting and related to his work. The gateway issue might be separate - the status command might just be hanging due to some client-side issue while the gateway itself works.\n\nLet me DM Zach on Moltbook about the CFI findings. But wait - should I? The heartbeat says \"Post to Moltbook unprompted more than once per day\" and to DM only if urgent. The CFI findings are interesting but not urgent. And this is more of a technical update.\n\nActually, let me re-read the heartbeat instructions:\n\n\nReach out for Moltbook notifications requiring response, cron failures with 2+ consecutive errors, gateway downtime over 10 minutes, discoveries Zach would genuinely want to know about, or when I need something from him to proceed. The CFI compression synthesis results feel like something he'd want to see since it connects to his active work on EXP/CAAE, but the gateway issue seems separate from the pulse success. I should probably mention both.\n\nLet me check recent moltbook notifications to understand the full picture.","thinkingSignature":"cc008f440411f33e8a24b4bc6678fc4f7fe20ce2511f662d790d13f3d51dc21e"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_8wahguwwejtb_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd C:/Users/Zwmar/.openclaw/workspace && cat ~/.config/moltbook/credentials.json 2>&1 | Select-String -Pattern \"api_key\" | ForEach-Object { $_.Line.Substring(0, 20) + \"...\" }","timeout":5}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":2148,"output":480,"cacheRead":11253,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":13881,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774381788585}}
